title: Grateful Dead Live at Frost Ampitheater on 1989-05-07

 1:  Aiko Aiko
 2:  Little Red Rooster
 3:  Bertha
 4:  Me and My Uncle
 5:  Mexicali Blues

10:  Victim or the Crime

Rex Foundation Benefit
Billy Kreutzmann's 43rd Birthday

reviews.review_text:
Built to Last Hey Now
Good spot for Bertha
4 tunes from Built To Last.
Good version of BTL, Not an easy tune to pull off
Weir is really reaching for the high notes on Picasso
Sneak in a Bird Song! (They space it nicely)
Kinda prefer to hear Victim then Foolish.
but liked both these tunes
Crazy Fingers!!!
Aside from Mardi Gras
 I don't think they played Aiko
and Man Smart too often in the same show.
He's Gone!
Just like so many times before...
